{"tid":2331993,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京新病例當局以「境外輸入確診病例關聯病例」稱呼　網友：加本土二字有那麼難麼？","createTime":"2020-12-19T09:01:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-19T12:06:33.000Z","uid":271829,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"864cb9f50b9408b02f0c60fd4c095d7cf87e84ce","tid":2331993,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:01:11.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n國家衞健委今日的通報，指遼寧省大連市昨日新增一宗「本地病例」，但對於北京的兩宗病例，卻是列為「境外輸入確診病例關聯病例」，北京的通報更強調，「無新增『本地』疑似病例和無症狀感染者」。<br />\n「北京的通報真的讓人迷惑！」這個超拗口的名詞一出，即時引發網民爭議：「首先這就是本土病例，搞甚麼關聯病例？還有說那麼多也說不清楚，怎麼感染的不講，行動軌跡也沒有！」「境外輸入不都是在閉環式（封閉式）隔離14天嗎？怎麼接觸到的？」「文字遊戲還是大首都會玩！」<br />\n...<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201219/ZBO6GTGHPBDFVJXEVTVP6ADFYI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201219%2FZBO6GTGHPBDFVJXEVTVP6ADFYI%2F&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBTcZFjLth35g1vO%2BxS%2F2N%2Fg%3D&h=03d76040\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201219%2FZBO6GTGHPBDFVJXEVTVP6ADFYI%2F&h=a1a8027d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201219/ZBO6GTGHPBDFVJXEVTVP6ADFYI/</a>"},{"pid":"39cf67cecac9248669443251ca7a9506b4460a68","tid":2331993,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:02:24.000Z","msg":"犯国安法，拉得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8534617cfbf20363653240e77a39e6684202c246","tid":2331993,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:02:40.000Z","msg":"2019新型冠狀病毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea23cc42ee613b9e6ac398d1bfc3c4f3ee6925de","tid":2331993,"uid":109923,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-19T09:03:52.000Z","msg":"咁全世界嘅